{"tid":810080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇00後既人都係咁？","createTime":"2018-09-07T16:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T23:36:42.000Z","uid":202227,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"84577339682e495ce7418919429b1d654444c072","tid":810080,"uid":202227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:10:41.000Z","msg":"每日朝早一醒 完全搵唔到生存意義 好攰<br />\n心好撚空 好孤獨 但唔寂寞 因為起碼仲有自己陪住自己<br />\n就算身邊有朋友 但都覺得所有人好虛偽<br />\n完全唔想出去面對一切 面對人 同人溝通 <br />\n連摺係屋企攤係將床都覺得好撚攰 好撚頹廢<br />\n就算平日要番學 番到去都係要笑住面對所有人 包括屋企人<br />\n番到屋企入番自己間房既時候 每秒都問緊自己：究竟我生存意義係咩？姐係點？dse考完就無生存目的？好鳩戇<br />\n我都好迷惘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416c4da37eb0da16d43eb7fb8e358dd37e6c6ba5","tid":810080,"uid":142854,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:15:34.000Z","msg":"得啦叻啦"},{"pid":"bbe1d44321835e86d19e53c7435ff4c7039d2c81","tid":810080,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:25:56.000Z","msg":"臭閪"},{"pid":"288670909d2bae7dcf4828c9d65761ac0624e1ff","tid":810080,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:13:20.000Z","msg":"做下運動啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62513d0b591f6eaa8683502a23bf904f1efbf794","tid":810080,"uid":166188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T22:15:03.000Z","msg":"中學雞感性時期"},{"pid":"fe917cc23f23a05f7151932d38dab7eca200f76a","tid":810080,"uid":125683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T22:18:43.000Z","msg":"ig呃like式文章"},{"pid":"bedea012a429a92171cd06c6e936fdfdc7d333da","tid":810080,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T22:20:01.000Z","msg":"系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：00絲"},{"pid":"168